Per-command JSON shapes: todo → {ok, specs, markers, edges, closures:[{hash, nodes:[{id,kind,filepath?,line?}], edges:[{from,to}], events:[{kind,nodeId?,edge?,oldHash?,newHash?,seed}]}], unlinkedMarkers}; list → {specs:[{id,filepath,deleted,unlinked,drifted,text?}], markers:[{id,filepath,startLine,endLine,deleted,unlinked,drifted,preview?}], edges:[{from,to,status}]}; show → {kind,id,filepath,hash,lines?,content,linked:[...]}; diff closure → {hash, diffs:[{kind,spec?,marker?}]}; diff --all → {closures:[{hash,events,diffs}]}; init/link/unlink/reset → {ok,command,message}; help/skill → {text}; version → {version}; errors → {ok:false,error,hint?,exit}. Each DiffSide has {id,filepath?,lines?,baselineHash,currentHash,hasBaseline,deleted,baseline?,current?,patch?}.